@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Portfolio";
}

<style>
    .page-section {
        display: none;
    }

    #home {
        display: block;
    }

    .profile-img {
        width: 250px;
        height: 250px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        object-fit: cover;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .skill-card {
        border: 1px solid #eaeaea;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        height: 100%;
    }

    .project-card {
        border: 1px solid #eaeaea;
        padding: 2rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .contact-table td {
        padding: 12px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea;
    }
</style>

<div class="container py-5">

    <section id="home" class="page-section">
        <div class="row align-items-center" style="min-height: 80vh;">
            <div class="col-md-7">
                <h1 class="fw-bold display-4">Nicholo John L. Batoy</h1>
                <h4 class="text-secondary mb-4">BSIT Undergrad</h4>
                <p class="text-muted mb-4" style="line-height: 1.8;">
                    Hi, I'm Nicholo John L. Batoy, a BSIT student at Lyceum of Alabang with a passion for technology and continuous learning. As an aspiring IT professional, I love sharpening my strategic thinking through developing applications, exploring software systems, and building responsive web solutions.
                </p>
                <a href="#projects" class="btn btn-primary px-4 me-2 nav-trigger">View Projects</a>
                <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-outline-secondary px-4 nav-trigger">Contact Me</a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5 text-center">
                <img src="~/images/my-photo.png" alt="Profile" class="profile-img">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about" class="page-section">
        <h2 class="text-center fw-bold mb-5">About Me</h2>
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-10 text-muted" style="line-height: 1.8;">
                <p>Hello! My name is Nicholo John L. Batoy, and I am currently a student at Lyceum of Alabang. I am pursuing a Bachelor of Science in Information Technology (BSIT), a choice driven by my fascination with technology and how it shapes our daily lives. Throughout my educational journey, I have been dedicated to building a solid foundation in tech concepts, and this course is providing me with the practical skills and knowledge needed to thrive in the digital age.</p>
                <p>Looking ahead, my ultimate career goal is to become a highly skilled IT professional, capable of tackling complex technological challenges. I am naturally curious, and one of my biggest interests is simply learning new things—whether that means picking up a new programming language or exploring how different systems work. Ultimately, my future plan is to secure a great job in the tech industry where I can grow professionally, while also making sure I take the time to truly enjoy life.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="skills" class="page-section">
        <h2 class="text-center fw-bold mb-5">Skills</h2>
        <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-md-3">
                <div class="skill-card">
